From MSFT on new OCR:

“Hi team,
 
Please find the release note for the latest Read container preview. Feel free to let us know if you have any questions.
 
Release Date:
• 5/20/2020
 
Image Path:
• *containerpreview.azurecr.io/microsoft/cognitive-services-read:1.1.012340006-amd64-preview (http://containerpreview.azurecr.io/microsoft/cognitive-services-read:1.1.012340006-amd64-preview)*
 
Quality Level:
• GA Candidate quality
• Suitable for customers preview
 
Resolved Issues (compared to container preview from earlier this month)
• Revert the model configuration to match with the earlier releases result (1.1.009920003-amd64-preview and 1.1.009910003-amd64-preview)
 
Known critical bugs:
• None at this point
”
